<!DOCTYPE html>
<html>
  <head>
    <title><%= title %></title>
    <link rel='stylesheet' href='/stylesheets/style.css' />
  </head>
  <body>
    <style>
    .grid {
        display: grid;
        grid-template-columns: repeat(auto-fit, minmax(300px, 1fr));
        gap: 1.5rem;
        margin-top: 2rem;
    }

    .card {
        background: var(--card-bg);
        backdrop-filter: blur(12px);
        border: 1px solid rgba(255, 255, 255, 0.1);
        border-radius: 20px;
        padding: 1.5rem;
        transition: transform 0.3s ease, border-color 0.3s ease;
    }

    .card:hover {
        transform: translateY(-5px);
        border-color: var(--primary);
    }

    .card-title {
        color: var(--text-muted);
        font-size: 0.9rem;
        font-weight: 600;
        text-transform: uppercase;
        letter-spacing: 0.05em;
        margin-bottom: 0.5rem;
    }

    .card-value {
        font-size: 2rem;
        font-weight: 700;
        color: var(--text-main);
    }

    .welcome-section {
        margin-bottom: 3rem;
    }

    .welcome-section h1 {
        font-size: 2.5rem;
        background: linear-gradient(to right, #fff, #94a3b8);
        -webkit-background-clip: text;
        -webkit-text-fill-color: transparent;
        margin-bottom: 0.5rem;
    }
</style>

<div class="welcome-section">
    <h1>Bem-vindo ao VendaMais</h1>
    <p>Sua plataforma de sucesso está pronta para escalar.</p>
</div>

<div class="grid">
    <div class="card">
        <div class="card-title">Usuários Ativos</div>
        <div class="card-value"><%= users %></div>
    </div>
    <div class="card">
        <div class="card-title">Vendas (Mês)</div>
        <div class="card-value">R$ <%= sales.toLocaleString('pt-BR', { minimumFractionDigits: 2 }) %></div>
    </div>
    <div class="card">
        <div class="card-title">Planos Ativos</div>
        <div class="card-value"><%= activePlans %></div>
    </div>
</div>
  </body>
</html>
